$k_stmts[] = $k_stmt_pre."(5, 35, '<p>This year we are bringing together our love of music to tell you a story. This story, although grand and beautiful, is not often told. It is vast in its telling and shows humanities depths through various musical aspects. We are delighted to be sharing with you the hope, joy, and celebration of music with the 2016-2017 music season.&nbsp;<br />\\r\\n<br />\\r\\n<u><strong>Concert Season</strong></u>&nbsp;<br />\\r\\n<br />\\r\\n<em><strong>&ldquo;From the Composer&#39;s Pen&rdquo;</strong></em>&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nFeaturing the Nixa High School Chamber Choir&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nSunday, October 30th, 3:00 p.m.&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nSchweitzer United Methodist Church&nbsp;<br />\\r\\n<br />\\r\\n<em><strong>Carol of the Angels&nbsp;</strong></em><br />\\r\\nFeaturing the music of Vivaldi, Saint-Saens, Britten and Rutter&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nTuesday, December 6th, 7:30 p.m.&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nAll Saints Anglican Church&nbsp;<br />\\r\\n<br />\\r\\n<em><strong>The Rest of the Story</strong></em>&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nLesser Known Works of the Great Composers&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nSunday, February 26th, 3:00 p.m.&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nBarnett Recital Hall on the campus of Evangel University&nbsp;<br />\\r\\n<br />\\r\\n<em><strong>The Story Never Ends</strong></em>&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nSunday, April 30th, 3:00 p.m.&nbsp;<br />\\r\\nRedeemer Lutheran Church</p>\\r\\n', 'This year we are bringing together our love of music to tell you a story. This story, although grand and beautiful, is not often told. It is vast in its telling and shows humanities depths through various musical aspects. We are delighted to be sharing with you the hope, joy, and celebration of music with the 2016-2017 music season. Concert Season From the Composer&#039;s Pen Featuring the Nixa High School Chamber Choir Sunday, October 30th, 3:00 p.m. Schweitzer United Methodist Church Carol of the Angels Featuring the music of Vivaldi, Saint-Saens, Britten and Rutter Tuesday, December 6th, 7:30 p.m. All Saints Anglican Church The Rest of the Story Lesser Known Works of the Great Composers Sunday, February 26th, 3:00 p.m. Barnett Recital Hall on the campus of Evangel University The Story Never Ends Sunday, April 30th, 3:00 p.m. Redeemer Lutheran Church');";
