$k_stmts[] = $k_stmt_pre."(6, 37, 'Since its beginning in 1966, Springfield Mid-America Singers has been one of the regions premier choral organizations. The group has become nationally recognized for its ambitious and versatile programming and outstanding performances. They perform four concerts per year, with auditions held each summer.', 'Since its beginning in 1966, Springfield Mid-America Singers has been one of the regions premier choral organizations. The group has become nationally recognized for its ambitious and versatile programming and outstanding performances. They perform four concerts per year, with auditions held each summer.');";
